{"tid":7472,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩佬告知曼聯高層：冬窗買買買！","createTime":"2016-11-28T00:01:00.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T03:43:48.000Z","uid":22985,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fb425e3b920c75115b3552ef7e87bee6ea1df8dc","tid":7472,"uid":22985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T00:01:00.000Z","msg":"　　今夏收購豪砸了1.8個億歐元之後，曼聯的整體陣容得到了提升，但摩連奴率領的球隊戰績卻是不盡如人意，聯賽與歐霸盃雙線潰敗，這讓曼聯高層感覺到了無奈。如今，冬季轉會期將至，摩連奴則是呼籲曼聯高層繼續給予資金上的支持來收購球員，明年1月繼續豪砸。<br />\n<br />\n　　「事實上，我們需要高質量的球員，但是你不可能在一個轉會窗之內，就把所有需要的球員都收攬齊了。」一位摩連奴身邊的密友，向《每日記錄報》透露說：「我們不可能一口氣就吃進4-5名需要的高質量球星。」"},{"pid":"c27a7e0d25ec57f09bfb1dcb8e8df2042ac9f49d","tid":7472,"uid":13718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T00:04:39.000Z","msg":"又買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aee3ddcd5f09a6fbda539c37a33b1c76414c4e4d","tid":7472,"uid":22985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T00:05:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n夏天用咁少錢點重建"},{"pid":"f3332833dff119cbe1560ef86cdb7e6ae21a3da2","tid":7472,"uid":4179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T00:07:50.000Z","msg":"仲可以買咩人？"},{"pid":"b54abb9936d6ad6dbde400ca376da5be6636930c","tid":7472,"uid":8157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T00:09:00.000Z","msg":"洗咁撚多錢仲好意思串我爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe4459a5e9d1c4b6d58718f2935837167fc60a45","tid":7472,"uid":760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T00:11:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洗咁撚多錢仲好意思串我爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/